Anagram Problems in DSA 
Two strings are anagrams if:
They contain exactly the same characters
Character frequency is the same
Order doesn't matter
listen
silent
Frequency
l -> 1
i -> 1
s -> 1
t -> 1
e -> 1
n -> 1
Both have identical frequency.
